    <stitle>FRONT DRIVE AXLE WHEEL ENDS: FABCO SDA-12 - DISASSEMBLY - BRAKE AND WHEEL SPINDLE REMOVAL</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc id="hl0201004" svcproctype="disassemble" graphiccount="1">
        <title>BRAKE AND WHEEL SPINDLE REMOVAL</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove brake group assembly. Support brake group to avoid brake being supported by the hose.
                Complete disconnect of brake hose would be better.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Hold the spindle, tap it with a soft hammer and it should separate from the spindle yoke as
                shown in
                <hotlnk xrefid="f0201020">Figure 20</hotlnk>.
            </para>
            <figure id="f0201020" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic filename="../figg02/G0201020.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 20. Removing Spindle Assembly</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the outer drive yoke from spindle yoke.</para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
